{"tid":551932,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴基之星肯退役未 咪撚出黎害人輸錢","createTime":"2018-02-06T05:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T04:50:31.000Z","uid":21488,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c25d8a2e8b41e9e5f282f25149706c6cdd551bdf","tid":551932,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"【巴基回勇】巴基之星通過首次試閘，還欠一次草閘合格就可復出<br />\n<br />\n性格巨星「巴基之星」繼早前在1800米草地試跳兩次合格後，今晨進一步向難度挑戰，出試第七組草地1600米大閘，結果馬匹在莫雷拉胯下刻意跟前，走過其「霸跑位」1400米時依然集中競走，最終更愈走愈勁，力壓廄侶「醒目名駒」率先以首名過終點返來，似乎這匹良駒不再玩性格，現時牠還欠一次草地1600米大閘合格，若然下次一樣順利通關，馬匹就可復出上陣。<br />\n對於今晨「巴基之星」試閘的表現，莫雷拉表示非常滿意，相信馬匹下次試閘亦可合格，而告東尼亦稱此馬鬥心復現，要試多一次草閘合格才可決定牠何時可復出上陣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有邊個100%保證佢到時唔會跑跑下停？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da17eb0495b4e1f57fca4b329f6e9f7f1eff1a0","tid":551932,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"攬住女皇盃第2 跑贏香港馬王明月千里退役咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af97d5e4c165bf52a8be83b19028da936c3fb087","tid":551932,"uid":4139,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"好撚掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee86b690160f578f75fdddb195a9960382cfa058","tid":551932,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"又比雷狗騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15696c0daa2b702781598124e058017339b7e32","tid":551932,"uid":67028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:48:19.000Z","msg":"佢都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20171219/57601189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin